## Results

### Phase 1 — PhiUSIIL (Native Training)

| Model | Accuracy | Precision | Recall | F1 | ROC-AUC |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Random Forest | 1.0000 | 1.0000 | 1.0000 | 1.0000 | 1.0000 |
| XGBoost | 1.0000 | 1.0000 | 1.0000 | 1.0000 | 1.0000 |

> Cross-validation confirmed: RF CV F1 = 1.0000 ± 0.0000 · XGB CV F1 = 1.0000 ± 0.0000

### Phase 2 — Cross-Dataset Evaluation

| Model | Setting | Accuracy | F1 | ROC-AUC |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Random Forest | Pretrained (no retraining) | 0.5000 | 0.0000 | 0.3917 |
| XGBoost | Pretrained (no retraining) | 0.5000 | 0.0000 | 0.4139 |
| Random Forest | Retrained on dataset_phishing | 0.8543 | 0.8513 | 0.9359 |
| XGBoost | Retrained on dataset_phishing | 0.8504 | 0.8473 | 0.9322 |

### Inference Speed & Model Size

| Model | Dataset | Inference Time | Model Size |
|---|---|---|---|
| Random Forest | PhiUSIIL | 3.2248s | — |
| XGBoost | PhiUSIIL | **0.2120s** | — |

